07:07.831 --> 07:17.581
saw who the leaders were on campus. Because the 
faculty, the first elections, I think clearly the

07:18.342 --> 07:31.255
faculty really became involved in it and elected 
the people they thought could best represent them

07:18.342 --> 07:31.255
in situations where they opposed the 
administrative structure. And so we had some

07:31.522 --> 07:36.228
pretty vocal people and some that weren't afraid 
to speak out. And it was an exciting time, exciting

07:36.909 --> 07:39.812
time. All right, let's jump back to your career. 
