07:58.893 --> 08:09.891
between eighteen and thirty, you know. Normally 
how did, in those early years particularly,

08:10.552 --> 08:17.924
normally how did you and a graduate student become 
related? Well, through my classes many times, I'd

08:18.245 --> 08:24.715
get to know students through classes, or contacts 
I was beginning to make in the field, or through

08:25.133 --> 08:32.022
some literature or something I had written. 
Someone would get in touch with me, want to study

08:32.463 --> 08:35.507
with me, those kinds of things. And I have had 
students over the years that have come to study,

08:35.607 --> 08:50.668
come to university to study with me, and that's 
